videos.description: Wake Forest finds the end zone on its opening drive as Jamie Newman fires a 9-yard touchdown to Sage Surratt.
videos.headline: Wake Forest QB grooves TD pass

videos.description: Memphis answers Wake Forest's opening touchdown drive with a score of its own via Tony Pollard's 41-yard touchdown burst.
videos.headline: Memphis RB bolts to house

videos.description: Memphis caps off a 98-yard touchdown drive on Damonte Coxie's 38-yard gain, setting up a score from Brady White to Patrick Taylor Jr.
videos.headline: Coxie's sick snag sets up Memphis TD

videos.description: Wake Forest QB Jamie Newman misfires and is intercepted by Chris Claybrooks, who chugs 37 yards to the house for a Memphis touchdown.
videos.headline: Newman's errant pass is picked for 6

videos.description: Memphis' Tony Pollard ties an NCAA record with his seventh career kickoff return touchdown on a 97-yard score in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Pollard ties NCAA record on 97-yard TD

videos.description: Jamie Newman breaks the plane on a 1-yard touchdown dive to pull Wake Forest within 11 points.
videos.headline: Newman plunges in for Wake Forest TD

videos.description: Wake Forest QB Jamie Newman muscles through multiple tackles en route to an emphatic 17-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Newman beasts into end zone on TD run

videos.description: Patrick Taylor Jr. takes the handoff and punches in a 9-yard touchdown, giving Memphis a 34-30 lead over Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Memphis regains lead with rush TD

videos.description: Jamie Newman's third rushing touchdown of the game gives Wake Forest a 37-34 lead over Memphis with 34 seconds left.
videos.headline: Wake Forest takes late lead on Newman's 3rd TD
